{"word":"G662 - ἀποτολμάω - apotolmáō - ap-ot-ol-mah'-o - Be very bold","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποτολμάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apotolmáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ot-ol-mah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be very bold</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தைரியங்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"to be bold of oneself"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G5111 - τολμάω - tolmáō - tol-mah'-o/5111\">G5111</a>; to <i>venture</i> plainly: - be very bold.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5111/5111\">G5111</a>, <a href=\"#/G5112/5112\">G5112</a>, <a href=\"#/G5113/5113\">G5113</a>, <a href=\"#/G662/662\">G662</a>"}]}